{"word":"G322 - ἀναδείκνυμι - anadeíknymi - an-ad-ike'-noo-mee - Appoint","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναδείκνυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anadeíknymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ad-ike'-noo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Appoint</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நியமி, தெரிந்துகொள்"},{"paragraph":"to lift up anything on high and exhibit it for all to behold, to show accurately, clearly, to disclose what was hidden"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G1166 - δεικνύω - deiknýō - dike-noo'-o/1166\">G1166</a>; to <i>exhibit</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>indicate</i>, <i>appoint:</i> - appoint, shew.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1165/1165\">G1165</a>, <a href=\"#/G1166/1166\">G1166</a>, <a href=\"#/G322/322\">G322</a>, <a href=\"#/G323/323\">G323</a>, <a href=\"#/G3856/3856\">G3856</a>, <a href=\"#/G5262/5262\">G5262</a>"}]}